Hello, my name is Maylen. A passionate Front-End Developer and UX/UI designer based in Sydney.

I'm passionate about travel, collaboration and shaping new designers through my activities as a blogger, speaker and course author.

I have 4 years of experience in designing and building highly scalable web applications. I mostly work with JavaScript, React JS, Node JS, GraphQL and Sketch. I'm also fluent with build tools like Webpack and Parcel, transpilers like Babel and Typescript, CIs like GoCD and Travis. I care a lot about user experience, minimalism, reusability and clean code.
